      <div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn">
        <p><lb n="1"></lb>kō-vicaiya-kampōtaArki y<unclear>ā</unclear> <lb break="no" n="2"></lb>ṇṭu Āṟ-āvatu</p>
        <p>m<choice>
            <orig>īy</orig>
            <reg>ī</reg>
          </choice>koṉṟai-nāṭṭu-p <lb n="3"></lb>puḷiyūr iruntu vāḻuñ cākāṭa <lb break="no" n="4"></lb>-c-ciṟṟaṉ puḷiyū<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied> Erumai koṇṭa <lb n="5"></lb>ñāṉ<unclear>ṟu</unclear> pūcal ōṭi mē <lb n="6"></lb>maṇikkala <gap quantity="4" reason="undefined" unit="character"></gap></p>
        <p>
          <lb n="7"></lb>
          <gap quantity="1" reason="undefined" unit="line"></gap>
        </p>
      </div>
